Robert B Easter

        reaster@comptechnews.com
        
Revision History                                                             
Revision 1.2           2000-01-04            Revised by: rbe                 


This miniHOWTO is about how to get the OpenGL/GLX Linux QuakeWorld client
compiled and working on systems with standard OpenGL hardware acceleration
support.

